data.description: Welcome Home! This four-bedroom, three-bath house of nearly 2500 sqft has an open floorplan that combines comfortable living with ample space. Boasting an all-brick exterior, the inside features a large living room, a dining room, an office with French doors, and a kitchen with modern appliances. The heart of this home is the breakfast bar, perfect for quick meals and snacks. The bedrooms have brand new carpet with plenty of natural light. Tile flooring in the living room, hallways, and office. The primary bedroom and bathroom feature two walk-in closets, a dual vanity, a walk-in shower, and a whirlpool tub. Outside, the home has a covered patio and fenced-in backyard, perfect for outdoor activities and relaxation. The 2-car garage provides ample parking space. Come and see this beautiful home today!
